jpnSearchText: ……！

engChrName: What a peculiar space...
engSearchText: What a peculiar space...
jpnChrName: この空間は………
jpnSearchText: この空間は………

engChrName: It's a terrifying sight to behold, and yet I feel...warm just being here.
engSearchText:
It's a terrifying sight to behold, and yet I feel...warm
just being here.
jpnChrName: なんでだろう…… こんな恐ろしげな光景なのに……
jpnSearchText:
なんでだろう……
こんな恐ろしげな光景なのに……

engChrName: I've never been to this place before, but I'm feeling oddly nostalgic.
engSearchText:
I've never been to this place before, but I'm feeling
oddly nostalgic.
jpnChrName: なんだか懐かしい感じがします……
jpnSearchText: なんだか懐かしい感じがします……

engChrName: Yeah. So nostalgic that it hurts.
engSearchText: Yeah. So nostalgic that it hurts.
jpnChrName: そうね…… ……泣きたくなるくらいに……
jpnSearchText:
そうね……
……泣きたくなるくらいに……
……ッ………

engChrName: Van!
engSearchText: Van!
jpnChrName: ──ヴァンさん！！
jpnSearchText: ──ヴァンさん！！

engChrName: \\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000You've gotta be kidding me... What are you idiots doing? You shouldn't be here.
engSearchText:
\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000You've gotta be kidding me...
What are you idiots doing? You shouldn't be here.
jpnChrName: ………馬鹿野郎共…………… ………どうして来やがった………
jpnSearchText:
………馬鹿野郎共……………
………どうして来やがった………

engChrName: \\u3000Thought I told you to take care of them, Master. Why'd you let them come to this place?
engSearchText:
\\u3000Thought I told you to take care of them, Master.
Why'd you let them come to this place?
jpnChrName: ……ベルガルド師父（せんせい）…… アンタの……仕業か………？
jpnSearchText:
……ベルガルド師父（せんせい）……
アンタの……仕業か………？

engChrName: You will have plenty of time to berate me for it later!
engSearchText: You will have plenty of time to berate me for it later!
jpnChrName: 焚き付けたのは確かだ！ 文句は後で幾らでも受け付けよう！
jpnSearchText:
焚き付けたのは確かだ！
文句は後で幾らでも受け付けよう！

engChrName: You can't leave us, Van!
engSearchText: You can't leave us, Van!
jpnChrName: それよりヴァンさんっ！ どうか勝手に行かないでくださいっ！
jpnSearchText:
それよりヴァンさんっ！
どうか勝手に行かないでくださいっ！

engChrName: This can't be the only way to deal with that demon! I refuse to accept that!
engSearchText:
This can't be the only way to deal with that demon!
I refuse to accept that!
jpnChrName: “魔王”だっけ！？ 何か方法はあるんじゃないの！？
jpnSearchText:
“魔王”だっけ！？
何か方法はあるんじゃないの！？

engChrName: Well, accept it. We're talking about a being that sees the entire world as its enemy.
engSearchText:
Well, accept it. We're talking about a being
that sees the entire world as its enemy.
jpnChrName: ………無駄だ…………… コイツは世界そのものに仇なす………
jpnSearchText:
………無駄だ……………
コイツは世界そのものに仇なす………

engChrName: I've felt its presence for so long... It's been with me since I was a kid.
engSearchText:
I've felt its presence for so long...
It's been with me since I was a kid.
jpnChrName: 昔から……ガキの頃から感じていた……
jpnSearchText: 昔から……ガキの頃から感じていた……

engChrName: \\u3000\\u3000But I couldn't tell anyone about it. It was a secret I planned to take to the grave.
engSearchText:
\\u3000\\u3000But I couldn't tell anyone about it.
It was a secret I planned to take to the grave.
jpnChrName: ……誰にも話せず…… ………てめえの胸だけに仕舞って………
jpnSearchText:
……誰にも話せず……
………てめえの胸だけに仕舞って………

engChrName: I can't destroy this thing, but I can seal it away in the boundary between here and the beyond.
engSearchText:
I can't destroy this thing, but I can seal it away
in the boundary between here and the beyond.
jpnChrName: だがあの彼方…… “外”への狭間へと封じ込めれば……
jpnSearchText:
だがあの彼方……
“外”への狭間へと封じ込めれば……

engChrName: It'll at least keep it at bay for a few centuries. That's the best I can do to protect your futures.
engSearchText:
It'll at least keep it at bay for a few centuries.
That's the best I can do to protect your futures.
jpnChrName: 滅ぼせなくても数百年くらいは ……大人しくさせられるだろう………
jpnSearchText:
滅ぼせなくても数百年くらいは
……大人しくさせられるだろう………

engChrName: \\u3000 So leave me be. This is the choice that I've made.  It's not a black-or-white decision. It's—
engSearchText:
\\u3000 So leave me be. This is the choice that I've made.
It's not a black-or-white decision. It's—
jpnChrName: これが俺の“選択”だ…… ………黒でも白でもなく──……
jpnSearchText:
これが俺の“選択”だ……
………黒でも白でもなく──……

engChrName: We're not going to leave you, Van!
engSearchText: We're not going to leave you, Van!
jpnChrName: 私たちだって同じです……！
jpnSearchText: 私たちだって同じです……！

engChrName: You may have chosen to come here of your own volition, but we've made a choice of our own. We're taking you back!
engSearchText:
You may have chosen to come here of your own
volition, but we've made a choice of our own.
We're taking you back!
jpnChrName: それが貴方の“選択”だと言うなら 私たちも“選択”してここへ来ました！
jpnSearchText:
それが貴方の“選択”だと言うなら
私たちも“選択”してここへ来ました！

engChrName: You know full well I'm not like the cops or bracers. I do things my own way.
engSearchText:
You know full well I'm not like the cops or bracers.
I do things my own way.
jpnChrName: 俺は警察でも遊撃士でもない。 あくまで自分の流儀を貫くだけだ。
jpnSearchText:
俺は警察でも遊撃士でもない。
あくまで自分の流儀を貫くだけだ。

engChrName: And that way isn't black, but it definitely ain't white, either. Mine's like the color of a dark blue sky just before dawn.
engSearchText:
And that way isn't black, but it definitely ain't
white, either. Mine's like the color of a dark blue sky
just before dawn.
jpnChrName: 黒でも白でも、灰色ですらない、 黎（あおぐろ）い狭間の領域で。
jpnSearchText:
黒でも白でも、灰色ですらない、
黎（あおぐろ）い狭間の領域で。

engChrName: I'm not going to become a wholly different person if I stay by your side.
engSearchText:
I'm not going to become a wholly different person if I
stay by your side.
jpnChrName: でも、そんな貴方を支えて 寄り添うことは出来ると思うんです。
jpnSearchText:
でも、そんな貴方を支えて
寄り添うことは出来ると思うんです。

engChrName: I'm very much my own woman, and that's not about to change.
engSearchText:
I'm very much my own woman, and that's not about
to change.
jpnChrName: まだまだ半人前ですけど あくまで私ならではの“色”で。
jpnSearchText:
まだまだ半人前ですけど
あくまで私ならではの“色”で。

engChrName: Your way isn't black, white, or even gray. You said it's like the color of the dark blue sky just before dawn...
engSearchText:
Your way isn't black, white, or even gray. You said it's
like the color of the dark blue sky just before dawn...
jpnChrName: 黒でもない、白でもない！ ましてや灰色ですらない──
jpnSearchText:
黒でもない、白でもない！
ましてや灰色ですらない──

engChrName: ...but to me, it's like the dawn itself. It's a warm, comforting light that illuminates our way and breaks through the darkest nights.
engSearchText:
...but to me, it's like the dawn itself. It's a warm,
comforting light that illuminates our way and
breaks through the darkest nights.
jpnChrName: 夜明け前の優しい暗がりみたいに 寄り添ってくれる貴方だけの色が──
jpnSearchText:
夜明け前の優しい暗がりみたいに
寄り添ってくれる貴方だけの色が──

engChrName: And I never want to part from that light again! We aren't going to let you go—no matter what!
engSearchText:
And I never want to part from that light again!
We aren't going to let you go—no matter what!
jpnChrName: どうしようもなく愛おしくて 何があっても失いたくはないから！！
jpnSearchText:
どうしようもなく愛おしくて
何があっても失いたくはないから！！

engChrName: You wanna up and leave us that bad, huh? Well, normally I'd say, 'Eh, that's your call. So long, my dude.'
engSearchText:
You wanna up and leave us that bad, huh?
Well, normally I'd say, 'Eh, that's your call. So long,
my dude.'
jpnChrName: ハッ、てめえが居なくなろうが 俺はどうだっていいけどな。
jpnSearchText:
ハッ、てめえが居なくなろうが
俺はどうだっていいけどな。

engChrName: But you've still got an outstanding debt, so I'm not letting you bail on me.
engSearchText:
But you've still got an outstanding debt, so I'm not
letting you bail on me.
jpnChrName: ただ貸し逃げは許さねえってだけだ。
jpnSearchText: ただ貸し逃げは許さねえってだけだ。

engChrName: Yeah! I'll drag you back by the collar if I have to!
engSearchText: Yeah! I'll drag you back by the collar if I have to!
jpnChrName: そうですっ……！ クルガの戦士としてもあり得ません！
jpnSearchText:
そうですっ……！
クルガの戦士としてもあり得ません！

engChrName: Let us help you, Van. You always stick your neck out for us, so why can't we return the favor?
engSearchText:
Let us help you, Van. You always stick your neck out
for us, so why can't we return the favor?
jpnChrName: 僕も同じかな……大体ヴァンさん、 いちいち矛盾してない？
jpnSearchText:
僕も同じかな……大体ヴァンさん、
いちいち矛盾してない？

engChrName: If we were in your shoes, you'd rush to our aid without a second thought! Don't deny it!
engSearchText:
If we were in your shoes, you'd rush to our aid
without a second thought! Don't deny it!
jpnChrName: 仮に僕たちが貴方と同じ立場だったら 絶対に放っておかないよねぇ？
jpnSearchText:
仮に僕たちが貴方と同じ立場だったら
絶対に放っておかないよねぇ？
………っ………………

engChrName: Heehee. I'm afraid he's got you there, Mr. Arkride. I can easily picture that happening.
engSearchText:
Heehee. I'm afraid he's got you there, Mr. Arkride.
I can easily picture that happening.
jpnChrName: ふふ……そうですね。 それだけは容易に想像が付きます。
jpnSearchText:
ふふ……そうですね。
それだけは容易に想像が付きます。

engChrName: If any of us were in danger, you would move heaven and earth itself to ensure our safety.
engSearchText:
If any of us were in danger, you would move heaven
and earth itself to ensure our safety.
jpnChrName: どれほどの困難があったとしても 疑問の入る余地すらなく。
jpnSearchText:
どれほどの困難があったとしても
疑問の入る余地すらなく。

engChrName: Once a softie, always a softie. Honestly, you should drop the whole 'I'm not good or bad' thing.
engSearchText:
Once a softie, always a softie. Honestly, you should
drop the whole 'I'm not good or bad' thing.
jpnChrName: あー、確かにそうでしょうね。 な～にが白黒付けないんだか。
jpnSearchText:
あー、確かにそうでしょうね。
な～にが白黒付けないんだか。

engChrName: You're just a teensy bit too young for the weary warrior act, don't you think?
engSearchText:
You're just a teensy bit too young for the weary
warrior act, don't you think?
jpnChrName: 苦み走ったクールキャラは まだちょっと早いんじゃないの～？
jpnSearchText:
苦み走ったクールキャラは
まだちょっと早いんじゃないの～？

engChrName: Everyone... Why...?
engSearchText: Everyone... Why...?
jpnSearchText: …………お前……ら………………

engChrName: You have actively forged many bonds throughout this year. I'm afraid this is simply karma at work.
engSearchText:
You have actively forged many bonds throughout
this year. I'm afraid this is simply karma at work.
jpnChrName: これがおぬしがこの世で為した 縁にして絆、そして業（カルマ）であろう。
jpnSearchText:
これがおぬしがこの世で為した
縁にして絆、そして業（カルマ）であろう。

engChrName: Don't think you can run away from them so easily, young man.
engSearchText:
Don't think you can run away from them so easily,
young man.
jpnChrName: ゆめ逃れられるなどと思わぬことだ。
jpnSearchText: ゆめ逃れられるなどと思わぬことだ。

engChrName: Master...
engSearchText: Master...
jpnSearchText: ………………師父（せんせい）………………

engChrName: Wh-What's happening?!
engSearchText: Wh-What's happening?!
jpnChrName: ！　ヴァンさん……！？
jpnSearchText: ！　ヴァンさん……！？

engChrName: \\u3000Damn it... This is way too soon!
engSearchText: \\u3000Damn it... This is way too soon!
jpnSearchText:
………クソが………………
…………早すぎるだろ…………

engChrName: \\u3000\\u3000Get out of here, now!  It's going to...
engSearchText:
\\u3000\\u3000Get out of here, now!
It's going to...
jpnChrName: いいから逃げろ……… ………このままじゃ…………！
jpnSearchText:
いいから逃げろ………
………このままじゃ…………！

engChrName: WHO HAS AWOKEN ME FROM MY SLUMBER? \\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000WAS IT YOU?
engSearchText:
WHO HAS AWOKEN ME FROM MY SLUMBER?
\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000WAS IT YOU?
jpnChrName: ───我ヲ目覚メサセタルハ汝等カ───
jpnSearchText: ───我ヲ目覚メサセタルハ汝等カ───

engChrName: It's talking directly into my mind...
engSearchText: It's talking directly into my mind...
jpnChrName: 頭に……響いて………
jpnSearchText: 頭に……響いて………

engChrName: What in the world... What's going on here?!
engSearchText: What in the world... What's going on here?!
jpnChrName: なによこれ……何なの……！？
jpnSearchText: なによこれ……何なの……！？

engChrName: IN THIS WORLD, I AM THE BEING KNOWN AS \\u3000\\u3000\\u3000THE VAGRANT DEMON LORD.
engSearchText:
IN THIS WORLD, I AM THE BEING KNOWN AS
\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000THE VAGRANT DEMON LORD.
jpnChrName: ───我ハコノ可能世界ニオイテ─── ───《漂泊ノ魔王》ト呼称サレシモノ───
jpnSearchText:
───我ハコノ可能世界ニオイテ───
───《漂泊ノ魔王》ト呼称サレシモノ───

engChrName: I AM CONNECTED TO THE ONE YOU CALL VAN ARKRIDE THROUGH A DIABOLIC CORE.
engSearchText:
I AM CONNECTED TO THE ONE YOU CALL
VAN ARKRIDE THROUGH A DIABOLIC CORE.
jpnChrName: ───《魔核（であぼりくこあ）》ヲ通ジテ─── ───ゔぁん・あーくらいどト繋ガッテイル───
jpnSearchText:
───《魔核（であぼりくこあ）》ヲ通ジテ───
───ゔぁん・あーくらいどト繋ガッテイル───

engChrName: The demon that's been residing within Mr. Arkride must have taken control!
engSearchText:
The demon that's been residing within Mr. Arkride
must have taken control!
jpnChrName: ヴァン様と一体化した “魔王”そのものの人格……！？
jpnSearchText:
ヴァン様と一体化した
“魔王”そのものの人格……！？

engChrName: B-But why? What happened to Van?
engSearchText: B-But why? What happened to Van?
jpnChrName: ど、どうしていきなり……！？
jpnSearchText: ど、どうしていきなり……！？

engChrName: MY FOOLISH VESSEL REBELLED AGAINST ME. \\u3000HE SOUGHT TO CHAIN ME TO THE VOID.
engSearchText:
MY FOOLISH VESSEL REBELLED AGAINST ME.
\\u3000HE SOUGHT TO CHAIN ME TO THE VOID.
jpnChrName: ───我ガ依代ガ許可ナク─── ───我ヲ无限（ムゲン）に繋ガントシタタメ───
jpnSearchText:
───我ガ依代ガ許可ナク───
───我ヲ无限（ムゲン）に繋ガントシタタメ───

engChrName: THE ENDLESS PASSAGE OF TIME HOLDS LITTLE MEANING TO A BEING SUCH AS MYSELF.
engSearchText:
THE ENDLESS PASSAGE OF TIME HOLDS
LITTLE MEANING TO A BEING SUCH AS MYSELF.
jpnChrName: ───星霜ノ刻ハ我ニ然程ノ意味ヲ持タヌガ───
jpnSearchText: ───星霜ノ刻ハ我ニ然程ノ意味ヲ持タヌガ───

engChrName: HOWEVER, SUCH BOUNDLESS ARROGANCE CANNOT GO UNPUNISHED.
engSearchText:
HOWEVER, SUCH BOUNDLESS ARROGANCE
CANNOT GO UNPUNISHED.
jpnChrName: ───ソノ度シ難キ傲慢ハ許シガタシ───
jpnSearchText: ───ソノ度シ難キ傲慢ハ許シガタシ───

engChrName: Ugh!
engSearchText: Ugh!
jpnChrName: ぐうっ……！！
jpnSearchText: ぐうっ……！！

engChrName: Get outta here!
engSearchText: Get outta here!
jpnChrName: ……フザけんな……ッ……！
jpnSearchText: ……フザけんな……ッ……！

engChrName: Yes! Will you kindly disappear already?!
engSearchText: Yes! Will you kindly disappear already?!
jpnChrName: そうです── ふざけないで下さいっ……！！
jpnSearchText:
そうです──
ふざけないで下さいっ……！！

engChrName: We were talking to Van—not you!
engSearchText: We were talking to Van—not you!
jpnChrName: 私たちはヴァンさんと 話しているんです……！
jpnSearchText:
私たちはヴァンさんと
話しているんです……！

engChrName: We don't care about you in the slightest!
engSearchText: We don't care about you in the slightest!
jpnChrName: 貴方が何者かはどうでもいい──
jpnSearchText: 貴方が何者かはどうでもいい──

engChrName: So get out of our sight...and return Van to us at once!
engSearchText: So get out of our sight...and return Van to us at once!
jpnChrName: どうか私たちの元に ヴァンさんを返してください……！！
jpnSearchText:
どうか私たちの元に
ヴァンさんを返してください……！！

engChrName: The Geneses are reacting?!
engSearchText: The Geneses are reacting?!
jpnChrName: ゲ、ゲネシスが！？
jpnSearchText: ゲ、ゲネシスが！？

engChrName: Wh-What's happening now?
engSearchText: Wh-What's happening now?
jpnChrName: な、なんなのよ……！？
jpnSearchText: な、なんなのよ……！？
─────ツ─────

engChrName: \\u3000\\u3000I SEE. SO YOU HAVE THEIR POWER AT YOUR DISPOSAL. THAT EXPLAINS HOW \\u3000THAT ㌍㌫㌻ WAS ABLE TO BIND ME.
engSearchText:
\\u3000\\u3000I SEE. SO YOU HAVE THEIR POWER
AT YOUR DISPOSAL. THAT EXPLAINS HOW
\\u3000THAT ㌍㌫㌻ WAS ABLE TO BIND ME.
jpnChrName: ───成程、彼ノ者ガ拵エシ絡繰カ─── ───道理デ㌍㌫㌻ノ“枷”ナドヲ許シタワケダ───
jpnSearchText:
───成程、彼ノ者ガ拵エシ絡繰カ───
───道理デ㌍㌫㌻ノ“枷”ナドヲ許シタワケダ───

engChrName: I think the Geneses are having an effect!
engSearchText: I think the Geneses are having an effect!
jpnChrName: き、効いてる……！？
jpnSearchText: き、効いてる……！？

engChrName: Yes. I can confirm that its strength has decreased.
engSearchText: Yes. I can confirm that its strength has decreased.
jpnChrName: ええ……霊圧が低下しました！
jpnSearchText: ええ……霊圧が低下しました！

engChrName: Good. I think Van's body is still somewhere inside of it.
engSearchText:
Good. I think Van's body is still somewhere inside
of it.
jpnChrName: 多分、ヴァンさんは あの身体の中心にいます……！
jpnSearchText:
多分、ヴァンさんは
あの身体の中心にいます……！

engChrName: We just need to weaken it a little more...
engSearchText: We just need to weaken it a little more...
jpnChrName: “この人”からの干渉を 少しでも弱められればきっと……！
jpnSearchText:
“この人”からの干渉を
少しでも弱められればきっと……！

engChrName: Ugh. Just let me at it, already! I'll rip it to shreds!
engSearchText: Ugh. Just let me at it, already! I'll rip it to shreds!
jpnChrName: ッ……よく分からんが……！！
jpnSearchText: ッ……よく分からんが……！！

engChrName: Our odds of victory have increased exponentially!
engSearchText: Our odds of victory have increased exponentially!
jpnChrName: そういう事ならば勝機もあろう──！！
jpnSearchText: そういう事ならば勝機もあろう──！！

engChrName: MANY EONS HAVE PASSED SINCE I LAST \\u3000ENTERED THE REALM OF MORTALS.
engSearchText:
MANY EONS HAVE PASSED SINCE I LAST
\\u3000ENTERED THE REALM OF MORTALS.
jpnChrName: ───ヨカロウ、久方ブリノ現界ダ───
jpnSearchText: ───ヨカロウ、久方ブリノ現界ダ───

engChrName: I WILL STRIKE DOWN ALL THAT STAND IN MY WAY. \\u3000FACE THE ABYSS, INSIGNIFICANT HUMANS.
engSearchText:
I WILL STRIKE DOWN ALL THAT STAND IN MY WAY.
\\u3000FACE THE ABYSS, INSIGNIFICANT HUMANS.
jpnChrName: ───小サキ者ドモヨ、打チ震エルガイイ───
jpnSearchText: ───小サキ者ドモヨ、打チ震エルガイイ───

engChrName: We'll show you who's insignificant!
engSearchText: We'll show you who's insignificant!
jpnChrName: っ…… 小さくても意地があるんですっ！！
jpnSearchText:
っ……
小さくても意地があるんですっ！！

engChrName: Your first and last mistake...is underestimating us humans!
engSearchText:
Your first and last mistake...is underestimating
us humans!
jpnChrName: 人間（あたしたち）の意地と力、 せいぜい味わってみなさい──！！
jpnSearchText:
人間（あたしたち）の意地と力、
せいぜい味わってみなさい──！！

engChrName: A crack appeared!
engSearchText: A crack appeared!
jpnSearchText: ……！　亀裂が……！

engChrName: Yes! Maybe Van can—
engSearchText: Yes! Maybe Van can—
jpnChrName: 良かった、これで……！
jpnSearchText: 良かった、これで……！

engChrName: OOOOOOOOOH!
engSearchText: OOOOOOOOOH!
jpnChrName: ───オオオオオオオオ────
jpnSearchText: ───オオオオオオオオ────

engChrName: INSOLENT VESSEL. YOU DARE \\u3000\\u3000\\u3000OPPOSE ME?!
engSearchText:
INSOLENT VESSEL. YOU DARE
\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000OPPOSE ME?!
jpnChrName: ───依代ヨ、刃向カウツモリカ───
jpnSearchText: ───依代ヨ、刃向カウツモリカ───

engChrName: Oh, I dare, all right! I'm bustin' outta here!
engSearchText: Oh, I dare, all right! I'm bustin' outta here!
jpnChrName: たりめーだこのボケがああああっ！！！
jpnSearchText: たりめーだこのボケがああああっ！！！

engChrName: Van!
engSearchText: Van!
jpnChrName: ヴァンさんっ……！！
jpnSearchText: ヴァンさんっ……！！

engChrName: Thank goodness!
engSearchText: Thank goodness!
jpnChrName: よくぞご無事で……！
jpnSearchText: よくぞご無事で……！

engChrName: Can you still fight?
engSearchText: Can you still fight?
jpnChrName: ム──動けるか！？
jpnSearchText: ム──動けるか！？

engChrName: Hell yeah. I'm in top form. Got a lot I wanna say to y'all...
engSearchText:
Hell yeah. I'm in top form. Got a lot I wanna say
to y'all...
jpnChrName: ええ、大丈夫です……！ 色々言いたいこともあるが──
jpnSearchText:
ええ、大丈夫です……！
色々言いたいこともあるが──

engChrName: ...but that can wait. We got a demon lord to slay, and I'm gonna need everyone's help to do it. Can you gimme a hand?!
engSearchText:
...but that can wait. We got a demon lord to slay,
and I'm gonna need everyone's help to do it.
Can you gimme a hand?!
jpnChrName: まさに千載一遇ってヤツだ！ お前ら、どうか力を貸してくれ！！
jpnSearchText:
まさに千載一遇ってヤツだ！
お前ら、どうか力を貸してくれ！！

engChrName: Do you even have to ask?
engSearchText: Do you even have to ask?
jpnChrName: もちろんだよ……！！
jpnSearchText: もちろんだよ……！！

engChrName: Since we're so nice, we'll do it on the house!
engSearchText: Since we're so nice, we'll do it on the house!
jpnChrName: 貸し借り抜きの大サービスでね！！
jpnSearchText: 貸し借り抜きの大サービスでね！！

engChrName: Leave all your support needs to me!
engSearchText: Leave all your support needs to me!
jpnChrName: 援護その他、お任せを……！！
jpnSearchText: 援護その他、お任せを……！！

engChrName: Here, Van. Catch!
engSearchText: Here, Van. Catch!
jpnChrName: ヴァンさん、これを……！
jpnSearchText: ヴァンさん、これを……！

engChrName: Thanks! Mare!
engSearchText: Thanks! Mare!
jpnChrName: ッ……悪いな！ ──メア！！
jpnSearchText:
ッ……悪いな！
──メア！！

engChrName: Well, look who's back. Just say the word, and I'll do my thing!
engSearchText:
Well, look who's back. Just say the word, and I'll do
my thing!
jpnChrName: まったく…… こっちは何時でも行けるわよ！
jpnSearchText:
まったく……
こっちは何時でも行けるわよ！

engChrName: Okay. Let's do this!
engSearchText: Okay. Let's do this!
jpnChrName: ああ、頼んだ！
jpnSearchText: ああ、頼んだ！

engChrName: Heh. I think it's time for the big, bad demon lord to kiss its ass goodbye! What do you say, Van?
engSearchText:
Heh. I think it's time for the big, bad demon lord to
kiss its ass goodbye! What do you say, Van?
jpnChrName: ハッ……そんじゃあ改めて “魔王退治”と行くかよ？
jpnSearchText:
ハッ……そんじゃあ改めて
“魔王退治”と行くかよ？

engChrName: Yeah...
engSearchText: Yeah...
jpnSearchText: ああ──……

engChrName: YOU TRULY ARE...AN IGNORANT VESSEL.
engSearchText: YOU TRULY ARE...AN IGNORANT VESSEL.
jpnChrName: ───依代ヨ、愚カナリ────
jpnSearchText: ───依代ヨ、愚カナリ────

engChrName: IF YOU THINK YOU CAN ESCAPE ME, \\u3000YOU ARE SORELY MISTAKEN.
engSearchText:
IF YOU THINK YOU CAN ESCAPE ME,
\\u3000YOU ARE SORELY MISTAKEN.
jpnChrName: ───我カラ逃レラレルト思ワヌコトダ───
jpnSearchText: ───我カラ逃レラレルト思ワヌコトダ───

engChrName: In some ways, that thing's an extension of myself.
engSearchText: In some ways, that thing's an extension of myself.
jpnChrName: ………ある意味、あれも俺自身だ。
jpnSearchText: ………ある意味、あれも俺自身だ。

engChrName: If you guys've got any pent-up anger toward me... then let it loose on that thing instead!
engSearchText:
If you guys've got any pent-up anger toward me...
then let it loose on that thing instead!
jpnChrName: 俺にぶつけるつもりだった怒り、 全力でブチかましてやれ──！！
jpnSearchText:
俺にぶつけるつもりだった怒り、
全力でブチかましてやれ──！！

engChrName: Will do!
engSearchText: Will do!
jpnChrName: 了解（ウーラ）っ……！！！
jpnSearchText: 了解（ウーラ）っ……！！！

engChrName: We won't allow you to hurt anyone else. Prepare to meet your end!
engSearchText:
We won't allow you to hurt anyone else. Prepare to
meet your end!
jpnChrName: ──今回ばかりは 遠慮なく行かせてもらいます！！
jpnSearchText:
──今回ばかりは
遠慮なく行かせてもらいます！！

engChrName: URRRRRRRRGH!
engSearchText: URRRRRRRRGH!
jpnChrName: ────オオオオオオオオオオオ────
jpnSearchText: ────オオオオオオオオオオオ────

engChrName: HOW COULD THIS BE? EVEN IN MY WEAKENED STATE, \\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000I SHOULD NOT HAVE BEEN BESTED.
engSearchText:
HOW COULD THIS BE? EVEN IN MY WEAKENED STATE,
\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000I SHOULD NOT HAVE BEEN BESTED.
jpnChrName: ────有リ得ヌ───── ────イカニ“枷”ト絡繰ガ有ルトハイエ────
jpnSearchText:
────有リ得ヌ─────
────イカニ“枷”ト絡繰ガ有ルトハイエ────

engChrName: Well, you were, so suck it up. No one likes a sore loser.
engSearchText:
Well, you were, so suck it up. No one likes a
sore loser.
jpnChrName: ま、今回はてめえの“負け”だ。
jpnSearchText: ま、今回はてめえの“負け”だ。

engChrName: 'Fraid I'm just not ready to give in to you yet. My body and soul are still mine, so do me a favor and scram.
engSearchText:
'Fraid I'm just not ready to give in to you yet.
My body and soul are still mine, so do me a favor
and scram.
jpnChrName: まだ呉（く）れてやるわけにはいかねえな。 ───この身体も、魂も。
jpnSearchText:
まだ呉（く）れてやるわけにはいかねえな。
───この身体も、魂も。
──────────────

engChrName: VERY WELL. I SHALL RETREAT FOR THE \\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000TIME BEING.
engSearchText:
VERY WELL. I SHALL RETREAT FOR THE
\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000TIME BEING.
jpnChrName: ────ヨカロウ、此度ハ退コウ────
jpnSearchText: ────ヨカロウ、此度ハ退コウ────

engChrName: BUT REMEMBER THIS: YOU AND I ARE ONE AND THE SAME—AND WE ALWAYS WILL BE.
engSearchText:
BUT REMEMBER THIS: YOU AND I ARE ONE
AND THE SAME—AND WE ALWAYS WILL BE.
jpnChrName: ─────サレド我ト汝ハ何処マデモ同ジ─────
jpnSearchText: ─────サレド我ト汝ハ何処マデモ同ジ─────

engChrName: AS LONG AS YOU LIVE, YOU WILL NEVER KNOW PEACE. \\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000YOU HAD BEST NOT FORGET THAT.
engSearchText:
AS LONG AS YOU LIVE, YOU WILL NEVER KNOW PEACE.
\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000\\u3000YOU HAD BEST NOT FORGET THAT.
jpnChrName: ─────ユメ忘レルナ───── ──────汝ニ安息ナド無イコトヲ──────
jpnSearchText:
─────ユメ忘レルナ─────
──────汝ニ安息ナド無イコトヲ──────
っ……！

engChrName: It's the diabolic core.
engSearchText: It's the diabolic core.
jpnSearchText: ……“魔核”か………

engChrName: Wha...?! Don't touch that!
engSearchText: Wha...?! Don't touch that!
jpnChrName: ！？……ダ、ダメですっ！
jpnSearchText: ！？……ダ、ダメですっ！

engChrName: We are NOT doing a repeat of last time!
engSearchText: We are NOT doing a repeat of last time!
jpnChrName: アンタ、まさかまたっ……！
jpnSearchText: アンタ、まさかまたっ……！

engChrName: Don't worry. I'm just putting this where it belongs.
engSearchText: Don't worry. I'm just putting this where it belongs.
jpnChrName: いや──折角の場所だ。
jpnSearchText: いや──折角の場所だ。

engChrName: RRAAAAAAAAAH!
engSearchText: RRAAAAAAAAAH!
jpnChrName: おおおおおおおおおおっ！！
jpnSearchText: おおおおおおおおおおっ！！
あ……

engChrName: H-He threw the damn thing?!
engSearchText: H-He threw the damn thing?!
jpnChrName: な、投げやがった……！？
jpnSearchText: な、投げやがった……！？

engChrName: Oh...
engSearchText: Oh...
jpnSearchText: ………ぁ………………

engChrName: Is it...finally over, then?
engSearchText: Is it...finally over, then?
jpnChrName: 終わっ……た……？
jpnSearchText: 終わっ……た……？

engChrName: Yeah.
engSearchText: Yeah.
jpnChrName: ああ………
jpnSearchText: ああ………

engChrName: At least, it's over for now. How 'bout we get outta here?
engSearchText:
At least, it's over for now. How 'bout we get
outta here?
jpnChrName: 今回の所は、な。 ──そろそろ戻るぞ。
jpnSearchText:
今回の所は、な。
──そろそろ戻るぞ。
